reviews.review_text: Overlooked? I haven't listened to the entire show yet, but this appears to be an overlooked In the Dark era show with a good setlist.  Sounds quality seems good for an AUD.

overlooked? Not by me but back then you had tapes...and where I was at, you basically got what you got through friends or at shows...I had this one...So I lived it over and over again..one of the top five in my rotation..again, that is from what tapes I had...
